OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early mist and fog quickly
OL,6,Fclearing to leave another dry day with
OL,7,Fplenty of sunshine. Some fair weather
OL,8,Fcloud will bubble at times, especially
OL,9,Fduring the middle of the day. Feeling
OL,10,Fwarm in the sunshine and light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining fine and dry this
OL,13,Fevening with some late sunshine.
OL,14,FPatchy cloud will tend to develop
OL,15,Fovernight with a few mist patches also
OL,16,Fforming.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FAnother dry and fine day
OL,19,Facross the region, with the best of
OL,20,Fthe sunny spells across the south.
OL,21,FFeeling warm once again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
