OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying fine, dry and very warm on
OL,7,FThursday and Friday. Likely to remain
OL,8,Fdry on Saturday although rain may
OL,9,Freach the area later in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
